parameters: To have such a beautiful woman in a man's room like this...
There's no need to worry about it
I don't mind, and I don't plan to stay long anyway
It was magic practice, right? Let's get started immediately
Then... the magic I've been practicing...
Please relax... and be ready to receive the magic...

Is it just my imagination...? There's a strange feeling in
my head...
Her eyes are open but... she's unconscious...
I did it... I did it...! The magic was a success...!\I[12]
The hypnosis magic I've been tirelessly practicing...!\I[12]
Now Alecia can be manipulated to my liking...!\I[12]
Alecia-san... you came to see me again...
Yes, I said I would join you for practice.
Rather, I should apologize for last time.
It's just that my memory is a bit hazy.

I probably failed, didn't I? It would have been better if I
could at least remember it.
No, no... It's not Alecia-san's fault...

Maybe my magic was poor... and that's why it didn't go
well...
So today... I'll make sure it succeeds, okay...?
Understood. Don't be afraid of failure and do your best.

(It's like something is flowing into my head... and it's
stronger than last time...)
Alecia-san...? Can you hear my voice...?
I've got the hang of it... I might be a genius...\I[12]

I cast it stronger than before... I should be able to push
it a bit more...\I[12]

What shall I have you do...? I'm looking forward to
it...\I[12]

It's already the third time, yet I have no memory of what
happened before.
Th-that's probably... because of the magic...
It's my fault for being clumsy... I'm so sorry...
Oh no, I didn't mean to blame you.
Right, it must be because of the failed magic.
Don't worry about it, as long as you succeed next time.
So, will you accompany me again today...?
Heheh... Then I'll take you up on that offer...
(I've got the hang of it now...)

(With this magic again... I'll make her lose
consciousness...)

(There's something I absolutely want to do... I'll make
Alecia mine...!)

(Has his magic improved? But he said it wasn't going
well...)

(I have a bad feeling about this magic... but at this rate,
my consciousness will...)

(I feel like something is breaking... I must stop it
immediately...)

(My consciousness is being taken away... it's no use... I
can't resist anymore...)

I've improved the magic from before... it's a super powerful
spell now...
In this state, I can do anything...\I[12]

The thing I absolutely wanted to do... I'm going to lose my
virginity...\I[12]
Tell me the truth, what are you hiding from me?
Stop lying, something is obviously off.

On top of my memory loss, I've been feeling strange in my
body lately.
It's all in your head... I only use wholesome magic...
Still going to deny it! You're shameless!

If that's how you want to play it, fine! I'll force the
truth out of you!
You bastard...! Using that magic again...!
Ugh... my head...! Stop it...! Right now...!

You've figured it out, huh...! I have no choice but to do
this...!

I'll make you fall with this magic...! You'll be completely
mine...!
Magic at full power...! Fall...! Fall for me...!
Stop, I'm telling you... my head is getting messed up...

Just endure this moment... If I can endure it, he'll have no
more tricks...
I won't fall for this... Who would ever do as you wish...!
How persistent... I can't... endure it anymore...

My magical power was at its limit too... If she had endured
even one more second...
But, but I made her fall... Now she's under my control...

I can't miss this chance... If the spell breaks, she might
kill me...

I will definitely corrupt her body...! \I[12]I'll make her
my woman...!\I[12]

Alecia\I[12]let's have sex\I[12]let's do it\I[12]I'll
cherish you with my beloved dick\I[12]

Even though no magic has been used...\I[12]my body can no
